This skill is an original design, not a port or fork of any existing skill.
The autonomous-loop concept that informed this skill traces back to
Karpathy's `autoresearch` (MIT) and to `alchaincyf/darwin-skill` (MIT)
which first applied the loop pattern to Claude Agent Skills, but the
architecture, gate function, A/B harness protocol, constitutional
judging mechanic, preference log schema, and self-trained-judge pipeline
scaffold are independent original work.

See NOTICE in this directory for design-influence attribution and
distinctions vs darwin-skill.

